description:
osu! is a free to play rhythm game featuring 4 modes, an online ranking system/statistics,
with user submitted songs downloadable from its website.

v0.1.2.description:
Changelog:
- Added 4 New Beatmap Packs:

  - "Vocaloid Pack"
  - "Touhou Pack"
- Added First YAML Options:
  - starting_songs
  - additional_songs
- Added "/download" Command to allow users to download beatmaps from a mirror.
- Drastically Reduced Filesize for the Slot Data by removing unused Keys, also allowing the apworld to be smaller despite having more songs.
- Fixed a Bug In which "/show_songs" could show the same song more than once.

v1.1.description:
## New Features
- Minimum Grade Option
- Disallow Converts Option
- Strict Difficulty Settings
  - Strict_Any - Only difficulties that fall in your difficulty ranges will send checks.
  - Strict_Random - A randomly chosen difficulty within your range has to be played.
  - Off works as the previous version did by default
- /save_settings, /load_settings, /save_all, /load_all commands.
  - Settings include Auto Download, Auto Track, and download type. Save/Load all affects both settings and keys.
- /check_diff to see which Difficulty of a given beatmapset is in logic.

## Fixes and Updates
- Song Data Caching for 3x faster loads (@Eijebong)
- Updated Song List
- Changed Direct Downloads to point to in-logic difficulties
- Updated API and fixed Daycore not counting as Difficulty Reduction (@Taoshix)
- Made /update async and able to autodownload (@Taoshix)
- Increased Auto Download Consistency
- Various Code Cleanups (@lilymnky-F and @Taoshix)

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/lilymnky-F/Archipelago-Osu/compare/v1.0.2...v1.1
